ch.epfl.sweng.smarteat

Class SuperTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.epfl.sweng.smarteat.SuperTest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DatabaseManagerTest, RestaurantCacheTest, RestaurantTest, SmartEatUserTest

    public abstract class SuperTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Adrien LAMIT on 12/11/16. For the course : Software Engineering at EPFL

    Base test for all tests that want to use the dependency injected values and mock them.

    Note that the mocks are reinitialized between each class of tests extending

      • setUp

        public void setUp()
        Sets up the tests to inject mock singletons. All of them are spies and will behave normally if not configured.

        Except database manager that will do nothing, RETURN_DEEP_STUBS configures it to return mocks for all its methods with return value. We also initialize facebook sdk in
